## Conversation
Stack PR 3/3: criterion 5 — remove the dockerized suite, run everything
clickhouse on the local backend.

## Actions
- Removed "Start ClickHouse" + "Run nox (Clickhouse Trace Server)" from
  test.yaml trace-tests and nightly-tests.
- nightly integration-only step now passes --trace-server=clickhouse-local:
  those shards run with NO marker filter, so their trace_server-marked tests
  hit the default clickhouse backend — previously served by the docker
  container at WF_CLICKHOUSE_HOST=localhost.
- Dropped dead WF_CLICKHOUSE_HOST envs and packages:write (existed solely for
  ch-image.sh GHCR mirroring) from these two jobs.

