## Hints for Future Agents
- KEEP: sqlite steps (sqlite backend ships in the product), migrator topology
  jobs (1s3r/2s2r genuinely need clusters; 1s1r uses keeper config),
  ch-image.sh (migrator jobs), and the docker fallback in
  ensure_clickhouse_db_container_running (local devs without a binary).
